---
layout: layouts/page
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
title: Now - Priyanshu Sinha
---
h2(class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold") Now
p(class="mt-6") What am I doing right now? Everything on here is automatically generated from various data sources.
div(class="mt-6 space-y-12")
    - recent =  lastfm.recentTracks[0]
    div(class="relative group overflow-hidden p-5 rounded-lg text-white")
        div(class="w-full h-full absolute top-0 left-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat group-hover:scale-125 transition-[transform] duration-300 ease-in-out scale-150 pointer-events-none blur-md" style=`background-image: url(${recent.imageUrl})`)
        div(class="relative w-full h-full z-10 space-y-3 bg-")    
            h3(class="font-medium text-zinc-100 text-xs") Last played:
            a(href=recent.url class="flex gap-4 items-center")
                img(src=recent.imageUrl class="h-16")
                div(class="flex flex-col")
                    p(class="text-lg font-semibold")= recent.track
                    p(class="text-sm text-zinc-100")= recent.artist

    div(class="space-y-6")
        h3(class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold") üíø Listening
        h4(class="text-zinc-700") My recently listened-to tracks, fetched from my #[a(href="https://www.last.fm/user/priyanshusinha7"  target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-900 hover:underline underline-offset-2") Last.fm] account.
        div(class="divide-y border rounded-lg overflow-hidden")
            each track in lastfm.recentTracks
                a(href=track.url target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="flex p-5 gap-3 items-center hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-color duration-300 ease-in-out")
                    img(src=track.imageUrl class="h-16")
                    div(class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 text-zinc-600")
                        h3(class="leading-tight text-base font-semibold text-black") #{track.track}
                        p= track.artist

    div(class="space-y-6")
        h3(class="text-2xl font-semibold") üçø Watching
        h4(class="text-zinc-700") The last 6 movies that I‚Äôve watched and (hopefully) enjoyed, recorded using #[a(href="https://letterboxd.com/priyanshusinha/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-900 hover:underline underline-offset-2") Letterboxd].
        div(class="divide-y border rounded-lg overflow-hidden")
            each movie in letterboxd
                a(href=movie.url target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="flex p-5 gap-2.5 group items-center hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-color duration-300 ease-in-out")
                    img(src=movie.imgSrc class="h-28")
                    div(class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 text-zinc-600")
                        h3(class="leading-tight text-base font-semibold text-black") #{movie.title}
                        p= `Release Year: ${movie.year}`
                        p= `Rating: ${filters.starRating(movie.rating)}`
include /footer
